description: Transform leftover turkey and stuffing into golden and crunchy air-fryer croquettes served with crispy parsley and cranberry mayo.
name: Air-Fryer Turkey & Stuffing Croquettes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place mayonnaise in a small bowl. Stir in sauce until almost combined. Scatter croquettes with crispy parsley and serve with mayonnaise mixture.
